## Phase 6's write rules (recap from `bash-no-go-zone.md`)

The foreman appends entries here using **Read + Edit**, NOT `cat >> file << 'EOF'`.

Reason: heredoc redirects trigger Claude Code permission prompts, which break the zero-interruption loop. Read this file → Edit at end → done.

